Pacifix looked up, it was time to get organized. He stood up from
thought, and developed his plan. "Good job Hoist." He turned to JetV.
"JetV, go introduce yourself to this robot, but be careful, take Artemis
with you. He turned to Sludge and Slag, "I don't even want to know where
Grimlock went, just begin patroling the perimiter." he said through
frustration. He then turned to Crossroads. "Suggestions?" He asked.

Crossroads looked thoughtful for a second. "Well, we will need a source
of energy, the wormhole destroyed our power reserves." Crossroads said
thinking over every option in his brain.

"Fine, Swoop, Repugnas, that's your job, find some energy, then report
back." Pacifix then turned around, twisted and contorted into his
transport mode, and began to ride off. "I need to check this planet
out."
